<h1 class="gutter-top" style="-ms-word-wrap: break-word; word-wrap: break-word;">
  D2L - Combine multiple course sections together in D2L
</h1>

<div id="ctl00_ctl00_cpContent_cpContent_divTags">
  <span class="sr-only">Tags</span>
  <span class="fa-solid fa-tags gray gutter-right-sm" aria-hidden="true" title="Tags"></span>
  
      <a href="/TDClient/180/Portal/KB/Search?SearchText=%2523faculty" id="ctl00_ctl00_cpContent_cpContent_rptTags_ctl00_TagControl1_lnkDisplay" title="faculty">faculty</a>

    
      <span class="fa-solid fa-circle gray gutter-right-sm font-xs vert-middle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    
      <a href="/TDClient/180/Portal/KB/Search?SearchText=%2523d2l" id="ctl00_ctl00_cpContent_cpContent_rptTags_ctl02_TagControl1_lnkDisplay" title="d2l">d2l</a>

    
      <span class="fa-solid fa-circle gray gutter-right-sm font-xs vert-middle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    
      <a href="/TDClient/180/Portal/KB/Search?SearchText=%2523CourseCombine" id="ctl00_ctl00_cpContent_cpContent_rptTags_ctl04_TagControl1_lnkDisplay" title="CourseCombine">CourseCombine</a>

    
</div>



<div id="ctl00_ctl00_cpContent_cpContent_divBody" class="gutter-top break-word ckeShim clearfix"><h2>How to combine multiple course sections together in SMSU D2L Brightspace site</h2>

<p>Faculty now have the ability to combine their courses in D2L Brightspace. All course merge requests (combining multiple course sections together) should be requested through the self-service</p>

<ol>
	<li>Login into your SMSU D2L Brightspace account<br>
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Click on Resources and then Course Self-Service in the upper left corner<img alt="Uploaded Image (Thumbnail)" data-image-url="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=88f7485d-80e0-4fa5-991e-b10cc618ae61.png&amp;beidInt=51" src="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=88f7485d-80e0-4fa5-991e-b10cc618ae61-thumb.jpg&amp;beidInt=51" style="display: block" title="Click to View Full Image"><br>
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li value="3">If prompted to login to SharePoint, please do by using your <a href="mailto:starid@minnstate.edu">starid@minnstate.edu</a> and starid password<br>
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li value="4"><em>Click</em> on <strong>My Courses</strong>.<img alt="Uploaded Image (Thumbnail)" data-image-url="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=8c09794d-8305-479b-8ade-f500f58205bd.png&amp;beidInt=51" src="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=8c09794d-8305-479b-8ade-f500f58205bd-thumb.jpg&amp;beidInt=51" style="display: block" title="Click to View Full Image"><br>
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li value="5">In the advance search option, go ahead and filter by the semester<img alt="" src=""><img alt="Uploaded Image (Thumbnail)" data-image-url="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=09249ee3-f0d3-4aff-9bed-9d1cf0855037.png&amp;beidInt=51" src="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=09249ee3-f0d3-4aff-9bed-9d1cf0855037-thumb.jpg&amp;beidInt=51" style="display: block" title="Click to View Full Image"><br>
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li value="6"><em>Select </em>the <strong>checkbox</strong> for each course section that you want to combine.<br>
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li value="7"><em>Click </em><strong>Combine</strong>.<img alt="Uploaded Image (Thumbnail)" data-image-url="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=7397a9c8-d266-4d20-a134-b9bb004575ce.png&amp;beidInt=51" src="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=7397a9c8-d266-4d20-a134-b9bb004575ce-thumb.jpg&amp;beidInt=51" style="display: block" title="Click to View Full Image"><br>
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li value="8"><em>Confirm </em>the merged course details.<br>
	<strong>Note: </strong>The section listed first is the ‘base’ course.&nbsp; Any course materials in the base course will be copied automatically into the new, merged course. <em>Click </em>the <strong>pin </strong>icon to adjust.<img alt="Uploaded Image (Thumbnail)" data-image-url="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=0074799a-ca50-40e6-b800-e6b8d49f6e14.png&amp;beidInt=51" src="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=0074799a-ca50-40e6-b800-e6b8d49f6e14-thumb.jpg&amp;beidInt=51" style="display: block" title="Click to View Full Image"><br>
	&nbsp;</li>
	<li value="9"><em>Type </em>the word <strong>merge</strong> into the confirmation field, and <em>click </em><strong>Merge.</strong><img alt="Uploaded Image (Thumbnail)" data-image-url="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=21c86b3e-7dc7-4130-9450-a356c8c81324.png&amp;beidInt=51" src="https://services.smsu.edu/TDPortal/Images/Viewer?fileName=21c86b3e-7dc7-4130-9450-a356c8c81324-thumb.jpg&amp;beidInt=51" style="display: block" title="Click to View Full Image">The merge request has been submitted.&nbsp; An email will be sent when the request has been processed.</li>
</ol></div>

